User instructions: 

Keyboard Typing trainer. 

Ensure your keyboard is in view of your webcam or camera. 
Press <button> to activate your camera.
Click and drag to line up the onscreen keyboard with your video feed.
Once aligned, Lock in the keyboard shape. 
Your hands will be recognized and a script will appear for you to type.
Type the script and the machine vision technology will analyze your hand posture (and WPM).


Other (possible) features: 
Freestyle typing mode.
Gaming version. 
